OL,3,CTheme park unveils new interactive
OL,4,Ccapybara experience
OL,6,FA theme park in east Sussex has
OL,7,Fcelebrated the opening of a new
OL,8,Finteractive capybara experience for
OL,9,Fvisitors.
OL,11,FThe Knockhatch Adventure Park, in
OL,12,FHailsham, unveiled its new attraction
OL,13,Fon Thursday at an official event,
OL,14,Fwhich was attended by the Mayor of
OL,15,FPolegate.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
