CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1776402250
OL,3,CTheme park unveils new interactive
OL,4,Ccapybara experience
OL,6,FVisitors who take up the 30-minute
OL,7,Fexperience will get a chance to feed
OL,8,Fand interact with the park's resident
OL,9,Fcapybara sisters, with the aim of
OL,10,Fproviding a broader understanding of
OL,11,Fherd dynamics.
OL,13,FZookeeper Ben Anderson, speaking to
OL,14,FITV Meridian, allayed any concerns
OL,15,Fthat people won't be able to get up
OL,16,Fclose and personal with the capybaras.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1776402250
OL,3,CTheme park unveils new interactive
OL,4,Ccapybara experience
OL,6,FHe said: "With capybara, being
OL,7,Freclusive isn't something we've got to
OL,8,Fworry about. We can almost guarantee
OL,9,Fthey're going to be coming up.
OL,11,F"The easiest way to their heart is
OL,12,Fthrough their stomach."
OL,14,FParticipants must be at least eight
OL,15,Fyears old and wearing suitable
OL,16,Fclothing - including fully enclosed
OL,17,Fshoes, long trousers and a full-
OL,18,Fsleeved top.
OL,20,FAnyone aged 16 or below also has to be
OL,21,Faccompanied by an adult.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
