PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1776402250
OL,3,CTheme park unveils new interactive
OL,4,Ccapybara experience
OL,6,FThe park says the experience will
OL,7,Fensure people "head off with a massive
OL,8,Fsmile and a much better idea of what
OL,9,Fmakes these curious creatures tick".
OL,11,FPrices for the attraction have not yet
OL,12,Fbeen shared by the park, although it
OL,13,Fhas confirmed entry into the rest of
OL,14,Fits premises will be included in the
OL,15,Ffee.
OL,17,FCapybara's have been a hot topic of
OL,18,Fconversation in recent weeks across
OL,19,Fthe country, after a female named
OL,20,FSamba, escaped from Marwell Zoo, in
OL,21,FHampshire.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
